text.tspan: Cumulative share of marriages in England and Wales ending in divorce
The cumulative share of marriages in England and Wales that had ended in divorce a given number of years
following the year of marriage. Each line represents a given cohort, marked by the year in which they were married
e.g. the line "1980" represents couples married in the year 1980.
Source: UK Office for National Statistics – Marriages and Divorces in England and Wales (2020)
